                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Report by the Deputies</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Deputies’ Report<note n="10" xml:id="d171fn10">The text of the Deputies’
                        Report is included in the United States Delegation Record of this meeting,
                            <hi rend="italic">supra</hi>.</note> was submitted to the Council by the
                    Chairman in office, who announced that the draft Treaty with Italy would be
                    distributed the same evening and the draft Treaties with Roumania, Bulgaria,
                    Hungary and Finland later, as and when they had been drawn up.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Agenda of the Council</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council fixed the Agenda of its proceedings and decided that it would deal in
                    succession with the following questions:— <list>
                        <item>Peace Treaty with Italy</item>
                        <item>Peace Treaty with Roumania</item>
                        <item>Peace Treaty with Bulgaria</item>
                        <item>Peace Treaty with Hungary</item>
                        <item>Peace Treaty with Finland</item>
                        <item>German questions</item>
                        <item>Austrian questions</item>
                        <item>Political situation in Italy</item>
                    </list>
                </p>
                <pb facs="0528" n="506" xml:id="pg_506"/>
                <p>The Soviet Delegation reserved the right to ask for the last question to be
                    discussed at any moment should political developments in Italy require it.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Peace Treaty with Italy</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It was agreed that the Deputies would draw up for each Council meeting the order
                    of the items suggested for consideration by the Ministers.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">IV. <hi rend="italic">Next Meetings</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It was agreed that the Council would hold its next meeting on Monday, 17th June
                    at 4 p.m. and that the Deputies would meet in the morning at 11 o’clock.</p>
